+ Handle Schema Inference\nand Evolution (Pipelines)
++ Auto Inference in Pipelines
+++_ from_json() with NULL schema
+++_ schemaLocationKey: schema storage key
+++_ Pipeline detects new fields automatically
++ Schema Evolution Modes
+++_ addNewColumns: auto-add new fields (default)
+++_ rescue: new cols → _rescued_data column
+++_ failOnNewColumns: fail on detection
+++_ none: ignore new columns
-- Rescued Data Column
---_ _rescued_data captures mismatches
---_ Prevents data loss
---_ Available for inspection + replay
-- Monitoring
---_ Pipeline event log
---_ Lakeflow Pipelines Editor (DAG)
---_ Configure failure notifications
@endmindmap
